channel.title: [PI] Noted Rocktails
channel.description: I added noted rock tails to my dspk server, but when I bank them or take them out of bank it still appears as noted rocktails, how can I make a unnoted version of this?

item.title: [PI] Noted Rocktails
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

baddy351:

You need to make sure that the rocktails are both the same thing, right now you server thinks they are 2 completely different models, so make sure your server sees that they are both considered rocktails (un-noted)

Or instead of thinking of the most complex answer…

Chances are, you don’t have the “unnoted” id in the server. So when you deposit/withdraw it doesn’t switch it to the correct version.
